body:
Hey, so pretty much after a lot of thinking I'm gonna take a break from Avicus for the main part, I will only be playing if my Team is having a scrim against a team but that will be pretty much it.

The reason for me wanting to take a break and not actually leaving is because I've gotten to know so many new people that I would consider my friends now I don't want to leave, I'll be thanking some people just in case my break goes on longer then expected.

This is not a leaving post I will be taking a break don'\t get fiesty with me..

Thank Yous,

Eric, You're one of my best friends and an amazing,kind, and funny person. You're like one of my many best friends and i don't know what I would do without you <3

Ashley/Tobin, First person from avicus that I've never gotten really mad at since I got back. I know you'll probably be the one to miss me the most on my break but don't worry I'll be back whenever my break ends/when I decide it is done.

Vice/Para/StepOnALegoMan, You made me almost have a heart attack when you said I was appealed after the year of me ban evading etc.. We've had some great times since I got back and we'll keep having them until we both step on a lego xD

Korea Team, You're like my family and best friends. When I first started the team I thought no one would join it but we've grown a lot in such little time even though we couldn't beat Apollo doesn't mean we're bad we just need to work harder as one. Love You Guys!

Staff Team, I know some of you are not very pleased with me or don't really like me but I understand that.. But I'll miss a lot of you guys even Eako (NOOB)


Rilo, you keep being a mop


Anyone else that I missed thank you for the great time since I got back :D

P.S I'll be spending my break on Hypixel and My Server (msg me if you ever want to play with me, also pls no lock ily )
